data.description: *** Unbelievable deal is ready for new owner to move in *** Captivating Tunbridge! Like a brand-new construction. 5 bedroom, 4 bath home on a daylight basement. Open floor plan features a formal living room / office with french doors. Formal dining room. Coffered ceiling and a cozy stacked stone fireplace with wood mantle in the great room. Gourmet kitchen complete with granite countertops, oversized island with bar stool seating, stainless steel appliances. White cabinets and beautiful tile backsplash complete the look. Large walk in pantry and mud room valet with cubbies. A bedroom on main connects to the full bath with granite countertops and tile flooring, a separate entrance for the perfect guest suite. Step up into the open loft , rail media room This is sure to be your family's favorite hang out room. Fabulous master suite with trey ceilings and double doors to the master bath. Luxurious 7 foot tile shower with frameless glass, dual shower heads, granite countertops, double bowl vanity and large walk in closet. Two of the upstairs bedrooms share a jack and jill bath. The 3rd upstairs bedroom features a large walk in closet and private bath. Enjoy the outdoors on the covered deck with fireplace and tv hookup. Beautiful private wooded lot. Walk from your home into Little Mulberry Park at the back of the neighborhood. Great park with 890 acres of fun! Lakes, hiking trails, playgrounds and pavillions. Wonderful community.
